51ac07cf22b34d27c9a3a135e9be0.mp4?t=1707321657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >To walk on the colored tiles you need to be in the same color...</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996710/extras/1e4ec80aff8a68d923e2e2e0f47c4512.poster.avif?t=1707321657\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996710/extras/1e4ec80aff8a68d923e2e2e0f47c4512.webm?t=1707321657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996710/extras/1e4ec80aff8a68d923e2e2e0f47c4512.mp4?t=1707321657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The cubes also need to be the color of the tile!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996710/extras/b90e04c81ad1736ce0f8caa298cb88c4.poster.avif?t=1707321657\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996710/extras/b90e04c81ad1736ce0f8caa298cb88c4.webm?t=1707321657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996710/extras/b90e04c81ad1736ce0f8caa298cb88c4.mp4?t=1707321657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You can remove the paint if you need to!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996710/extras/c39e331a6c4d65644a8c4ce71bf2b02d.poster.avif?t=1707321657\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996710/extras/c39e331a6c4d65644a8c4ce71bf2b02d.webm?t=1707321657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source s